name: Commander Keen 6: Aliens Ate My Baby Sitter!
name_original: Commander Keen 6: Aliens Ate My Baby Sitter!
description:
Commander Keen 6: Aliens Ate My Baby Sitter! is an arcade game developed by id Software. It came out on 20-12-1991. FormGen published the game. The game is rated as "Recommended" on RAWG.
Commander Keen 6: Aliens Ate My Baby Sitter! is available on PC.
Tom Hall directed the game. It was scored by Robert Prince.
